<F P=100> ITALY &amp; VATICAN CITY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Bomb Blast Damages Padua Social Security Office </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3112111693 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1004 GMT 
31 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD3112111693 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Italian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Following the recent bomb attacks at the law court 
and the Northern League office, a bomb exploded last night at 
the provincial office of the National Agency for Social Security 
on Piazza Insurrezione [in Padua, northern Italy]. 
  A rudimentary device exploded at around 0300 shattering the 
two large windows of the office, damaging the ceiling, and one 
of the main doors. 
  Police went quickly to the scene after being alerted by 
local 
residents who were woken up by the blast. 

</TEXT>

