<H3> <TI>   Spokesman Calls Turkish Reports on Shooting Unfounded </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0401123894 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 1130 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0401123894 </F>
