<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Greek </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Government spokesman Ioannis Kasoulidhis rejected as 
entirely unfounded Turkish allegations that shots were fired on 
the confrontation line. Mr. Kasoulidhis said that these 
allegations, which have not been confirmed by the UNFICYP [UN 
