<F P=102>  TA0401120994 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1100 
GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0401120994 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of Turkish map with </F>
statistical figures] 
  [Text] The inflation rate in 1993 was 71.1 percent. 
During December, prices increased by 3.6 percent. According to 
a statement issued by the State Statistics Institute, the 
consumer price index increased by 71.1 percent and the wholesale 
price index by 60.3 percent in the past year. In December, 
consumer prices rose by 3.6 percent, while wholesale prices 
registered an increase of 2.9 percent. 

