<H3> <TI>   EU's Delors, Commissioners Arrive for Talks </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0401194294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in 
Greek 1800 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0401194294 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network </F>


