  [Excerpt] Jacques Delores, European Union [EU] Commission 
president, and EU commissioners arrived at Ellinikon Airport a 
short time ago and, without making any statements, left 
immediately for the Grande Bretagne Hotel. Prime Minister 
Andreas Papandreou will host a dinner in Delors' honor. 
Alternate Foreign Minister Theodhoros Pangalos welcomed the EU 
commissioners. 
  Delors and Papandreou will meet tomorrow to discuss the 
general guidelines for implementing the white paper on 
development, employment, competition, and foreign policy issues. 
[passage omitted] 

