<F P=100> CYPRUS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Welcomes Remarks by EC's Delors </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0501183194 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 1700 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0501183194 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Greek </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Foreign Minister Alekos Mikhailidhis described the 
statement by [EC Commissioner] Jacques Delors as encouraging and 
positive for Cyprus regarding both the Cyprus issue and the 
application for Cyprus' accession to the European Union. In a 
statement to CyBC [the Cyprus Brodcasting Corporation], 
Mikhailidhis said he hoped Delors would also actively support 
his positions, especially now, when Cyprus will seek to insure a 
date for opening negotiations on its accession to the Community. 

</TEXT>

