<H5>  Techniques Used by SOFRES </H5>
  1. Poll conducted by LE FIGARO MAGAZINE. 
  2. Date conducted: 23-25 November 1993. 
  3. National sample of 1,000 persons, representative of the 
entire population 18 years and over, interviewed in person at 
their respective residences by the network of SOFRES 
interviewers. 
  4. Method of classification (sex, age, profession of head of 
household PCS [employer, manager, employee]); grouping by region 
and by category of populated area. 

